On the 17th and 23rd, the svc-app-rlct account got locked due to six incorrect password attempts. After checking with both the AD and network teams, it turns out the source could be any one of over 1,200 IPs, which makes it extremely difficult to isolate the exact origin. We've also reviewed our own logs, but there’s no clear indication that any of our servers are sending incorrect credentials. Given this, we’re focusing on preventive measures instead to avoid similar issues going forward